title: Cerebral Ballzy "City Girl" : Converse Red Light Sessions
description:
During CMJ 2013, Brooklyn based punk band popped joined Red Light Radio in their pop-up studio at Rubber Tracks to perform this gritty version of "City Girl" for Red Light Sessions.

Red Light Sessions are special live performances filmed in partnership with Amsterdam-based digital radio station Red Light Radio.
